These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, blue, brown, ebony
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, fish, snake
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up, tea, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, bartender, social-worker, musician
1. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the snake##1
2. the person drinking tea is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes ebony##2
3. the person drinking 7up is the pilot##1
4. the musician is on the left of the pilot##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the social-worker is the person who likes brown##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
9. the person who likes blue is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Color   | blue | ebony   | lavender  | brown  |
| Pet   | rat    | snake    | lizard      | fish    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | 7up | tea | cola |
| Job     | musician  | pilot       | bartender    | social-worker     |

