.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, canasta, snooker
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, dutch, australian, argentine
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, november, august, october
House: townhouse, cape-cod, modern, colonial
1. the colonial house is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is the cape-cod house##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the argentine is between the person who's birthday is in august and the townhouse house##2
6. the colonial house is between the argentine and the person who's birthday is in october##2
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
8. the dutch is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
9. the australian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Game         | snooker | monopoly    | canasta  | bridge    |
| Nationality   | brazilian      | dutch  | argentine  | australian |
| Birthday           | october      | august       | november      | february       |
| House         | cape-cod    | colonial | modern | townhouse |

