.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, ebony, brown, aquamarine
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, tulip, rose, poppy
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, egyptian, brazilian, canadian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, pall-mall, bluemaster, prince
1. the brazilian is the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the canadian##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
6. the egyptian is the person who growspoppy##1
7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
8. the person who likes ivory is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growspoppy##2
9. the person who growsrose is between the person who likes brown and the egyptian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Color        | ebony | brown     | ivory   | aquamarine     |
| Flower       | tulip   | begonia   | rose | poppy |
| Nationality         | italian   | brazilian | canadian       | egyptian    |
| Cigar   | bluemaster    | pall-mall | tiparillo  | prince    |

