There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, juice, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, bus, ship, snowmobile
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, tulip, balloon-flower
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking tea is the person who likes coral##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person driving the bus##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who likes pink##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 9. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person who likes chestnut is between the person driving the taxi and the person who likes amber##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Color           | coral  | amber | chestnut     | pink |
| Beverage   | tea | hot-chocolate  | juice | iced-tea       |
| Transport           | bus       | snowmobile    | ship      | taxi           |
| Flower         | poppy | zinnia   | balloon-flower   | tulip         |

