.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, cola, lemonade
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, april, october, december
4 different games are played: billiard, snooker, scrabble, whist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, rock, house, punk
 1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 2. the fan soul is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is the person drinking water##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the fan house##1
 5. the person playing whist is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person drinking cola is between the fan punk and the person playing billiard##2
10. the person playing scrabble is the fan house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage          | water         | cola         | iced-tea     | lemonade      |
| Birthday           | october | december | july    | april     |
| Game   | billiard      | scrabble       | whist    | snooker       |
| Music-Genre         | soul     | house       | punk | rock |

