.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, fonseca, game, swisher
City: nizza, colone, rome, hannover
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, purple, blue, lavender
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, almond-milk, lemonade
1. the person traveling to nizza is between the person drinking lemonade and the person traveling to rome##2
2. the fonseca-smoker is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who likes lavender##2
3. the person who likes blue is between the person drinking tea and the person who likes purple##2
4. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
5. the person who likes blue is the person who likes blue##1
6. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person who likes purple is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
8. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
9. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Cigar           | game | fonseca | old-henry  | swisher |
| City   | colone      | hannover       | nizza     | rome      |
| Color   | lavender   | purple      | blue   | white   |
| Beverage         | almond-milk   | lemonade    | fanta | tea   |

