There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, lilac, amber, turquise
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, papaya, garlic, lime
City: prague, berlin, rome, new-york
 1. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 2. the fisherman is the person eating garlic##1
 3. the person who likes lilac is between the person eating garlic and the person traveling to rome##2
 4. the person who likes amber is the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the person eating lime is on the left of the software-developer##1
 6. the fisherman is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 7. the person eating cranberry is the person traveling to prague##1
 8. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1
 9. the fisherman is on the right of the videographer##1
10. the person eating garlic is the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job   | videographer | fisherman | analyst  | software-developer  |
| Color   | blood-red       | amber   | lilac | turquise    |
| Food   | cranberry   | garlic   | lime | papaya |
| City     | prague    | new-york   | berlin    | rome  |

