 3. the german is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the swisher-smoker is the person driving the taxi##1
 6. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the american is on the left of the german##1
 8. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
 9. the russian is between the australian and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Transport          | airplane        | snowmobile    | taxi | scooter   |
| Nationality           | australian | russian | american   | german |
